{"tid":618722,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解板燒雞腿包咁辣？","createTime":"2018-04-06T04:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T05:11:11.000Z","uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96fb6d8116840391d620786aa6b08984daff9b20","tid":618722,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"唔食得辣的手足小心中伏！！"},{"pid":"17c9f94e813f6f05691aff2eefc349311cf23954","tid":618722,"uid":120972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"f8cc00af5edb4341574895c760f758698b279a3a","tid":618722,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:50:57.000Z","msg":"很多人都以為，吃太辣只會傷害腸胃，事實上，吃太辣也可能傷害膀胱。美國泌尿科臨床研究權威Dr. Robert. M. Levin指出，膀胱內膜非常敏感、脆弱，如果吃墨西哥辣椒等過於辛辣食物，經過代謝，其中物質很容易傷害膀胱內膜細胞，若原本膀胱機能就不好，或有間質性膀胱炎等疾病，吃太辛辣會讓症狀更加惡化。"},{"pid":"34216622bf530c10c4e16ec2a1a2dbdb6845d81f","tid":618722,"uid":2692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"劣質野先要整色整水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5507445ce87d75a204facfab6b5bee62dcb2d5ce","tid":618722,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"渣ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8ab5b645fe7c3c585b0b19d14ad84fa2126c0c","tid":618722,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96fb6d8116840391d620786aa6b08984daff9b20","tid":618722,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"唔食得辣的手足小心中伏！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"引你買多杯雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}